'''Methuen''' is a British publishing company. Its Canadian branch has published several [[:Category:Calendars|Tolkien calendars]] in Canada. They differ little to none from the international editions by [[Allen and Unwin|George Allen & Unwin]].

'''Calendars published:'''
* 1976: ''[[The Hobbit Calendar 1976|The Hobbit Calendar]]''
* 1979: ''[[The 1979 Calendar of J.R.R. Tolkien's The Lord of the Rings (Canada)|The Calendar of J.R.R. Tolkien's The Lord of the Rings]]''
* 1979: ''[[The Silmarillion Desk Calendar 1979|The Silmarillion Desk Calendar]]''
* 1981: ''[[The 1981 J.R.R. Tolkien Calendar - The Lord of the Rings (Canada)|The J.R.R. Tolkien Calendar]]
* 1984: ''[[The J.R.R. Tolkien Calendar 1984|The J.R.R. Tolkien Calendar]]''
* 1986: ''[[The 1986 Tolkien Calendar|The J.R.R. Tolkien Calendar]]
